				</script><div id="accordions-3151" class="accordions flat"><div class="accordions-head">Cancellation Policy<i class="accordion-icons accordion-plus arrow-dark"></i><i class="accordion-icons accordion-minus arrow-dark"></i></div><div style="font-size:13px;color:#444444" class="accordion-content"><p>In the unfortunate event that you can not attend after you've bought your ticket, we will refund you 90% of your ticket price and hold 10% to cover associated fees incurred on our part. Please contact tickets@udaya.com for cancellations.</p>
</div><div class="accordions-head">What is the last day to cancel?<i class="accordion-icons accordion-plus arrow-dark"></i><i class="accordion-icons accordion-minus arrow-dark"></i></div><div style="font-size:13px;color:#444444" class="accordion-content"><p>Tickets cancelled by July 17, 2016 will be refunded full amount, minus $100.00 processing fee. No cancellations after July 18, 2016 will be accepted. Cancellation requests should be sent to <a href="mailto:tickets@udaya.com" target="_blank"> tickets@udaya.com </a> .</p>
</div><div class="accordions-head">Can I get single day tickets?<i class="accordion-icons accordion-plus arrow-dark"></i><i class="accordion-icons accordion-minus arrow-dark"></i></div><div style="font-size:13px;color:#444444" class="accordion-content"><p>Absolutely! Single day passes will be available. More info coming soon.</p>
</div><div class="accordions-head">Do you offer group rates?<i class="accordion-icons accordion-plus arrow-dark"></i><i class="accordion-icons accordion-minus arrow-dark"></i></div><div style="font-size:13px;color:#444444" class="accordion-content"><p>For groups of 12 or more please contact <a href="mailto:tickets@udaya.com" target="_blank"> tickets@udaya.com </a> for group rates.</p>
</div><div class="accordions-head">Is airfare included in my festival pass price?<i class="accordion-icons accordion-plus arrow-dark"></i><i class="accordion-icons accordion-minus arrow-dark"></i></div><div style="font-size:13px;color:#444444" class="accordion-content"><p>No. You will need to purchase your own plane ticket.</p>
</div><div class="accordions-head">If I am unable to attend, can I transfer my festival pass into a friend’s name ?<i class="accordion-icons accordion-plus arrow-dark"></i><i class="accordion-icons accordion-minus arrow-dark"></i></div><div style="font-size:13px;color:#444444" class="accordion-content"><p>Yes, we offer a one time transfer of a festival pass to a friend or family member. If you need to transfer your festival pass please email <a href="mailto:tickets@udaya.com" target="_blank"> tickets@udaya.com </a> .</p>
</div></div><style type="text/css">
	
