				{
					
					$("#accordions-3139.accordions").accordion({
						collapsible: true,
						heightStyle: "content",
						animated: "swing",
						active: "",changestart: function(event, ui) {
							child.accordion("activate", false); 
						}
					});
					
					var child = $(".child-accordion").accordion({
						active:true,heightStyle: "content",
						collapsible: true,
						animated: "swing",

					});
				})

				</script><div id="accordions-3139" class="accordions flat"><div class="accordions-head">Travel Information<i class="accordion-icons accordion-plus arrow-dark"></i><i class="accordion-icons accordion-minus arrow-dark"></i></div><div style="font-size:13px;color:#333333" class="accordion-content"><p>If you are flying in to Sofia International Airport (SOF), a shuttle will be waiting to transport you (and your crew) to the Hotel Rila. Once you have purchased your ticket please make sure to send us your travel itinerary. Upon arrival at SOF, look out for our an Udaya Live Spirit Guide, who will lead to the shuttle and on your way to the festival. </p>
</div><div class="accordions-head">Lodging Information<i class="accordion-icons accordion-plus arrow-dark"></i><i class="accordion-icons accordion-minus arrow-dark"></i></div><div style="font-size:13px;color:#333333" class="accordion-content"><p>The Hotel Rila will be our home for the duration of the Yoga & Music Festival, all bookings will be taken care of with the purchase of your <a href="https://udayalive.com/purchasepass/">Festival Pass</a>. The resort is a 4 Start facility, fully remodeled this year, with an incredible spa and indoor pool facing the mountain. Prepare yourself for a unique festival experience in a retreat setting. </p>
</div><div class="accordions-head">What are the lodging options?<i class="accordion-icons accordion-plus arrow-dark"></i><i class="accordion-icons accordion-minus arrow-dark"></i></div><div style="font-size:13px;color:#333333" class="accordion-content"><p>Quads, Double, and Single Rooms are available. All rooms are equipped with cable TV, A/C, telephone, radio, hair dryer, and include complimentary laundry service. </p>
</div><div class="accordions-head">Where is Bulgaria?<i class="accordion-icons accordion-plus arrow-dark"></i><i class="accordion-icons accordion-minus arrow-dark"></i></div><div style="font-size:13px;color:#333333" class="accordion-content"><p>Bulgaria is a country in southeastern Europe. It is bordered by Romania to the north, Serbia and Macedonia to the west, Greece and Turkey to the south, and the Black Sea to the east.</p>
</div><div class="accordions-head">What airport to I fly into?<i class="accordion-icons accordion-plus arrow-dark"></i><i class="accordion-icons accordion-minus arrow-dark"></i></div><div style="font-size:13px;color:#333333" class="accordion-content"><p>Sofia International Airport (SOF) in Bulgaria</p>
</div><div class="accordions-head">Do I need a Passport?<i class="accordion-icons accordion-plus arrow-dark"></i><i class="accordion-icons accordion-minus arrow-dark"></i></div><div style="font-size:13px;color:#333333" class="accordion-content"><p>Yes! Unless your passport is from Bulgaria, you will need a passport to enter the country. *Please note: all passports must be valid at least six months from your date of  travel.</p>
</div><div class="accordions-head">Do I need a travel visa?<i class="accordion-icons accordion-plus arrow-dark"></i><i class="accordion-icons accordion-minus arrow-dark"></i></div><div style="font-size:13px;color:#333333" class="accordion-content"><p>For up to date information on travel visas to Bulgaria visit the <a href="http://www.bulgaria-embassy.org/webpage/Consular%20Information/visa/visa.htm" target="_blank"> Bulgarian Embassy </a> website.</p>
</div><div class="accordions-head">Where is the Hotel Rila?<i class="accordion-icons accordion-plus arrow-dark"></i><i class="accordion-icons accordion-minus arrow-dark"></i></div><div style="font-size:13px;color:#333333" class="accordion-content"><p>The Rila Hotel, 2010 Borovets Resort</p>
<p>(+359 750) 32 295<br />
<a href="http://www.rilaborovets.com/" target="_blank"> RilaBorovets.com </a></p>
</div><div class="accordions-head">What time is hotel check in & check out?<i class="accordion-icons accordion-plus arrow-dark"></i><i class="accordion-icons accordion-minus arrow-dark"></i></div><div style="font-size:13px;color:#333333" class="accordion-content"><p>We have secured a special check in and check out time for all of our festival goers.</p>
<p>Check in on August 18th ­ 11am</p>
<p>Check out on August 22nd ­ 5pm</p>
</div><div class="accordions-head">Does the Hotel have Wi­Fi?<i class="accordion-icons accordion-plus arrow-dark"></i><i class="accordion-icons accordion-minus arrow-dark"></i></div><div style="font-size:13px;color:#333333" class="accordion-content"><p>Yes!</p>
</div><div class="accordions-head">What if my flight arrives late in the day on August 18th?<i class="accordion-icons accordion-plus arrow-dark"></i><i class="accordion-icons accordion-minus arrow-dark"></i></div><div style="font-size:13px;color:#333333" class="accordion-content"><p>No problem. If you reserved our shuttle we will be waiting for you regardless of what time you land. You also might consider arriving the day before so you can be there for the opening ceremony and full festival program. Complimentary shuttle service is also available on August 17th, however hotel accommodation for that night is not included.</p>
</div><div class="accordions-head">What if I want to stay longer or arrive early?<i class="accordion-icons accordion-plus arrow-dark"></i><i class="accordion-icons accordion-minus arrow-dark"></i></div><div style="font-size:13px;color:#333333" class="accordion-content"><p>Contact Hotel Rila directly to book extra nights.</p>
<p>The Hotel Rila, 2010 Borovets Resort, Bulgaria</p>
<p>Dessi Kinova ­<a href="mailto:dkinova@bt-ds.com/" target="_blank"> dkinova@bt-ds.com</a></p>
<p>+359 2 8055546</p>
</div></div><style type="text/css">
	
